<li><strong>New Hampshire Rebate Program:</strong> The state offers rebates up to \$3,500 for renewable energy installations, including solar panels and certain high-efficiency HVAC systems. These rebates are administered through the New Hampshire Public Utilities Commission and are available on a first-come, first-served basis with annual funding limits.</li>
